{"tid":565231,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"孫 佳 君 祝 福 老 外 舊 愛 與 梁 芷 珊 新 戀 情","createTime":"2018-02-18T18:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T09:55:52.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"445096998ab5bd627d9b996918c48abaeb30933a","tid":565231,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:14:39.000Z","msg":"現年49歲的梁芷珊被爆跟羅傑承去年已離婚，原因不涉第三者，主要因兩人性格不合，身為商人的羅傑承是工作狂，梁芷珊卻是藝術家，3年前婚姻出現問題，梁芷珊長期失眠致暴瘦，可惜最後都是無力挽救！離婚後兩人再見亦是朋友，報道指回復單身的她，在飯局中認識了孫佳君舊愛法籍三星米芝蓮大廚Olivier，火速再墮愛河，女兒都贊成媽咪拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑承和梁芷珊分別透過秘書回覆雜誌，承認去年已離婚，女兒由大家共同撫養。羅傑承更指不清楚前妻新戀情，但會送上祝福。孫佳君對於舊愛與梁芷珊拍拖，她以短訊回覆：「噢，很久沒有聯繫過了，我很遺憾聽到離婚的消息。不過，我很高興聽到他們正在交往。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180215/large/15ec1p53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180215%2Flarge%2F15ec1p53.jpg&h=efbbf029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180215/large/15ec1p54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180215%2Flarge%2F15ec1p54.jpg&h=e57ef930&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06eccc338d580203aa392a0fb2693a9685cdad1d","tid":565231,"uid":48460,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T20:08:51.000Z","msg":"90後表示篇文入面全部人名都未聽過"},{"pid":"74d1b0381896acb9e520acf7673a1b751010d8f7","tid":565231,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"個鬼佬幾有男人味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbf3d50de56b76c567660184815acd4f7c73fae","tid":565231,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74d1b0381896acb9e520acf7673a1b751010d8f7","tid":565231,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"個鬼佬幾有男人味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" cla